    "subject": "Added unit test for TimelineMetricCache precision updates",
    "body": "This is a unit test for the TimelineMetricCache class. It tests the functionality of the getAppTimelineMetricsFromCache method when the cache is updated with precision values. The test method creates a mock configuration object and sets its properties to simulate the behavior of the `TimelineMetricCache` class when it receives a request to update a metric that has precision values. The test method then verifies that the cache is updated correctly with the precision values. The test method uses JUnit and Mockito frameworks to create the mock configuration object and set its properties. The test method also uses the `TimelineMetricCache` class to update the cache with precision values and then retrieves the updated metrics from the cache. The test method asserts that the retrieved metrics have the expected precision values."
}

