    "subject": "Added support for setting OS family type",
    "body": "This commit adds support for setting the desired OS family type using the `setFamily` method. The possible values for the OS family type are 'dos', 'mac', 'netware', 'unix', and 'windows'. The `eval` method determines if the OS on which Ant is executing matches the type set in `setFamily`. This commit also provides a method to set the desired OS family type and determine if the OS on which Ant is executing matches the type set."
