    "body": "This commit adds support for overwriting existing destination files when the `forceOverwrite` attribute is set to `true`. This feature allows users to update existing translation files without having to manually delete them first. The `forceOverwrite` attribute is added to the `Translate` class, and it defaults to `false`, meaning that existing files will not be overwritten unless explicitly requested. The `translate` method is modified to check for changes in the source files and associated resource bundles, and to overwrite the destination files if necessary. This change ensures that the translation process is efficient and effective, and that users can easily update their translation files as needed."
}

